video.title: Storage Wars: Texas
video.synopsis: The stakes are high and the drama intense in the Lone Star State as A&E's top-rated non-fiction franchise Storage Wars follows five Dallas storage unit hunters in their quest for auction gold.

episodes.synopsis: Lesa finds a curious snakeskin ensemble, Victor takes a big risk on a scooter, and Ricky and Bubba use their country roots to get a leg up.
episodes.title: Snake, Rattle, and Roll

episodes.synopsis: Lesa pins her hopes on an old cookie jar, Moe goes after medieval-looking items, and Ricky and Bubba miss out when they opt not to buy.
episodes.title: Remember the Alamo?

episodes.synopsis: Ricky and Bubba acquire a dubious collection of football players' autographs, and a cache of high-end furniture sparks an intense bidding war.
episodes.title: If I Were a Tibettin' Man

episodes.synopsis: Hoping to score big by acquiring high-end art and furniture, Jerry takes the reins from Lesa; Bubba's claustrophobia jeopardizes his bottom line.
episodes.title: Fandom of the Opera

episodes.synopsis: On the hunt for Western memorabilia, Lesa makes a discovery that gives her a leg up, and Ricky and Bubba turn to a cowboy for advice.
episodes.title: Dallas Cowboys and Indians

episodes.synopsis: Lesa bids against a former NFL player for a unit, Victor wins a treasure chest with no key, and a piece of genuine American history comes to light.
episodes.title: Who Bought JFK?

episodes.synopsis: The buyers face a choice: Should they go to an auction at a moderately but reliably profitable location, or go for broke in a developing neighborhood?
episodes.title: A Fistful of Auctions

episodes.synopsis: Hoping for a big payday in an affluent town, Ricky and Bubba look at tea party paraphernalia, and Lesa and Victor lock horns over a player piano.
episodes.title: High Tea Tighty

episodes.synopsis: With the pressure on in back-to-back auctions, Jerry persuades Lesa to buy a unit against her better judgment; Victor finds some old poker gear.
episodes.title: For a Few Lockers More

episodes.synopsis: Victor scores big with his unit, Ricky and Bubba snag a trove of sci-fi collectibles, and Lesa and Moe square off over a unit with a mystical item.
episodes.title: Bounty Hunter Bubba Fett

episodes.synopsis: In Dallas, Moe goes after some artwork, Victor gets more than he bargained for with his unit, and Ricky and Bubba eye a vintage air compressor.
episodes.title: Texas Sold 'Em

episodes.synopsis: Facing competition from scores of rival buyers, Moe gets creative with his locker, and Lesa and Ricky square off over a unit filled with power tools.
episodes.title: Mo' Money, Moe Prigoff

episodes.synopsis: A wealthy businessman's units spark fierce competition among the buyers for antique kitchen gear and other items with enormous profit potential.
episodes.title: The Good, the Bad, and the Hungry

episodes.synopsis: Things get bizarre when Moe looks for curios, Victor and Lesa bid on a pricey store display, and Ricky and Bubba find an electric hemorrhoid cushion.
episodes.title: Home on the Strange

episodes.synopsis: With $50,000 on the line, Lesa and Jerry land some old roping gear, Ricky and Bubba use a connection to get a leg up, and Victor gets devious.
episodes.title: Puffy in the Sky with Diamonds

episodes.synopsis: With a tornado bearing down, Jerry and Lesa find radioactive items, Victor tries to get Moe to pass on a locker, and Ricky and Bubba bid on a table.
episodes.title: The Surgeon, the Witch, and the Wardrobe
